Package com.jimmyselectronics.necchi

package com.jimmyselectronics.necchi
Welcome to Jimmy's Electronics, your one-stop shopping experience for high quality electronic components.

Our Necchi line of barcode scanners is the preferred choice for discerning friends of mine. Handheld units and combinations with electronic scales from our Virgilio line, your satisfaction will be more than supercazzora!

Jimmy's Electronics LLP
